eshmun.expression.visitor.visitors

Class FillDocumentVisitor

  • java.lang.Object
    • eshmun.expression.visitor.visitors.FillDocumentVisitor
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Visitor

    public class FillDocumentVisitor
extends java.lang.Object
implements Visitor
    Visitor for syntax colorizing and indentation of an AbstractExpression into a Document (java swing).

    1.0
    Author:
    Kinan Dak Al Bab
